      • marry

        public boolean marry(Test.Person person)
        This method checks gender of persons. If genders are not equal - tries to marry. If one of them has another spouse - execute divorce(sets spouse = null for husband and wife. Example: if both persons have spouses - then divorce will set 4 spouse to null) and then executes marry().
        Parameters:
        person - - new husband/wife for this person.
        Returns:
        - returns true if this person has another gender than passed person and they are not husband and wife, false otherwise
